<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
        <title>An Error Occurred: {{ status_text }}</title>
        <style>
           .trace {
                margin-bottom: 18px;
                background: #f7f7f9;
                border: 1px solid #e1e1e8;
                padding: 8px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                -moz-border-radius: 4px;
                display: block;
                font-size: 12.05px;
                white-space: pre-wrap;
                word-wrap: break-word;
                color: #333;
                font-family: Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;
                margin-left: 0px;
               }
            .trace ul {
               list-style: none;
               }
            .trace ul li {
               line-height: 12px;
               margin-bottom: 0px;
               }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Oops! An Error Occurred</h1>
        <h2>The server returned a "{{ status_code }} : {{ status_text }}".</h2>

        <div>
            Something is broken. <br>Please e-mail us at [email] and let us know
            what you were doing when this error occurred. <br>We will fix it as soon
            as possible. <br>Sorry for any inconvenience caused.
        </div> <br>
        
        <div class="">
            {{ exception|printDump }}
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
